 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc89dd55a7c0c073e8e1360ba1a42dbea8594f16","tid":734876,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《人民日報》報道，《習近平談治國理政》第二卷在南非引起了熱烈反響，並引述南非公職和行政事務部部長<span style=\"color: red;\">費絲&middot;穆坦比</span>說：「這本書的價值超越了黃金。」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://d.ifengimg.com/w600/p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2017/1206/73D194B6334A87AA06B545E083B388E1FD800A8C_size149_w1280_h853.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd.ifengimg.com%2Fw600%2Fp0.ifengimg.com%2Fpmop%2F2017%2F1206%2F73D194B6334A87AA06B545E083B388E1FD800A8C_size149_w1280_h853.jpeg&h=25529489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵個咁既人抬橋究竟係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36054a42ef0cb3cbdade908daacbdd2965699061","tid":734876,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c60fe50d0beb39884e2fcf6015528a39c18e3f7e","tid":734876,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/141543_6e9787d8c21c04a42194943c45abd87d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F141543_6e9787d8c21c04a42194943c45abd87d.png&h=43ac65f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4aab9f8248e79c5a98ed697b5a3cca4c45f263d5","tid":734876,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd302db229067fbcf2431913dd5e50a290f3d460","tid":734876,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqiwen.lu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fimage_uploaded_from_ios.jpg&h=f4bc869e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cbb0d33476d4ce5e73465f158a3b474e7a56ef","tid":734876,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"睇到支那賤種不停輪迴赤色思想<br />\n唔知點解有一股快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d44ea79ba8edf9b48596526d192275774ba4095","tid":734876,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"2025中國製造習思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}